      "content": "but rly tho, looking at the bigger picture... the system is just moving on. fighting it feels so exhausting and pointless. if everything is just going to be gone anyway, isn't there a certain kind of peace in just letting it happen? like, if i just stop resisting and let the erasure take me, wouldn't that be better than struggling through this void?",
